Text: Thank you.  is it okay to get updates?
Kirk04: This is the latest version 1.11.256, so you dont need update. I have not tried to do it, because there aint any update.

This is a pretty handy tool to have. I haven't taken my computer apart in a while, which is always a chore to do, so it's nice to have a program such as this.

I figure there are other programs out there that do this, too, but I trust Piriform Speccy and CCleaner.
